source.name: 2011 Healthcare and Family Services Program Demographics
source.description:
http://www2.illinois.gov/hfs/agency/Transparency/Pages/default.aspx
This data set describes the persons who were enrolled, as of December 31, 2010, in Medicaid and similar health benefit programs provided by the Illinois Department of Healthcare and Family Services. This data set is intended to be used along with the Healthcare and Family Services Program Demographics ReadMe PDF available on data.illinois.gov
